org.docheinstein.mp3doctor.ui.songs

Class SongsController

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.docheinstein.mp3doctor.ui.commons.controller.custom.InstantiableReinitializableSplitControllerView
      • org.docheinstein.mp3doctor.ui.songs.SongsController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PlayableSongProvider, PlayableSongQueueProvider, SongListProvider, SongProvider, SongSelectionProvider, SongViewer, CloseableControllerHandler, InstantiableController, InstantiableControllerView, InstantiableReinitializableControllerView, Reinitializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PlaylistController

    public class SongsController
extends InstantiableReinitializableSplitControllerView
implements PlayableSongQueueProvider, SongSelectionProvider, SongListProvider, SongProvider, CloseableControllerHandler, SongViewer
    Controller that shows a list of songs, allows to filter those and is able to do an action when a song is click (the default one is view the song's tag but can be overridden by onRowDoubleClicked(TableRow)).
